{"tid":1575316,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"成立維穩委員會","createTime":"2019-09-16T21:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T09:02:36.000Z","uid":118951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d1349911c942098641b43df1f15d5136cb4852","tid":1575316,"uid":118951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T21:47:47.000Z","msg":"明報委託港大既民調顯示，有約70.8%受訪者贊成港共最少要成立獨立調查委員會先收貨<br />\n<a href=\"http://link.mingpao.com/60242.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flink.mingpao.com%2F60242.htm&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rTXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=74d74fa8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Flink.mingpao.com%2F60242.htm&h=1649a678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://link.mingpao.com/60242.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>再次証明獨立調查委員會係各派既最大公約數</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭見此如果醒少少就會用盡政治能量去搞個委員會出黎<br />\n<br />\n而個委員會有幾種可能，但本質都係唔針對政治制度，只求解散我地既維穩委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以見到林鄭話搞乜委員會、無論用乜名義要醒水，因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根本問題係個政治制度</span></strong>，改革完警隊以後有咩政治矛盾始終都係要放班popo咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yjOAA1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yjOAA1.jpg&h=2825260f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下係我推測既兩大可能同簡單分析，可以唔睇<br />\n=================================<br />\n1.結構上搞諸多小動作既廢物委員會：<br />\n小動作可以係唔獨立、無法律效力、建制派主導、最後由林鄭拍板、調查示威者為主、傾計會等等，總之就做show畀外面既人睇顯示誠意就算<br />\n例如湯渣驊呢種：<br />\n<a href=\"https://simonshen.blog/2019/08/18/%E3%80%8C%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E8%88%87%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8Dvs%E3%80%8C%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9A%E9%AD%9A%E7%9B%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsimonshen.blog%2F2019%2F08%2F18%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%259B%25B8%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%258Dvs%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25AD%259A%25E7%259B%25AE%2F&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rTXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=9d6615e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://simonshen.blog/2019/08/18/%E3%80%8C%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E8%88%87%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8Dvs%E3%80%8C%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9A%E9%AD%9A%E7%9B%AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.真正既獨立委員會：<br />\n其實我想話呢招先毒...唔係話唔應該調查，但因為會好多人包括自己友會無左個動力、會收貨（未必真係缺一不可），佢肯做就等同收解散我地<br />\n留返最勇武唔妥協果一批都會無左正當性<br />\n問題係佢無根本上既制度改變，而激發呢場抗爭既首先係政府"},{"pid":"9ddf31982b69c86f7ffe32b743830de044ebb5b8","tid":1575316,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T21:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期三有大綱睇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rTXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=48e40b0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rTXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=906ff667\" data-auto-link target=